      | risk aversion | tau  | mu | r   | sigma |
      | 0.001         | 0.01 | 0  | 0.0 | 2     |
    And the price monitoring named "price-monitoring-1":
      | horizon | probability       | auction extension |
      | 1000000 | 0.999999999999999 | 300               |
