      | party | market id | side | volume | price | resulting trades | type       | tif     | reference |
      | aux   | ETH/DEC19 | buy  | 10     | 140   | 0                | TYPE_LIMIT | TIF_GTC | bestBid   |
      | aux2  | ETH/DEC19 | sell | 10     | 160   | 0                | TYPE_LIMIT | TIF_GTC | bestOffer |
